MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

96-2391. State v. Dougherty.

Hancock App. No. 5-94-2. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hancock County. Upon consideration of the notice of the death of John Robert Dougherty filed by counsel for appellant, and counsel’s request that this appeal be dismissed,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the request for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.
